#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:255
msgid "It is not a true PDF file!"
msgstr "Bu gerçek bir PDF dosyası değil!"

#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:258
msgid ""
"The PDF is password protected.\n"
"\n"
"If you have introduced the password, make sure it is the correct one.\n"
"\n"
"Otherwise, please go to NVDA configurations, TesseractOCR options and mark "
"the checkbox 'Ask for password'"
msgstr ""
"PDF parola korumalıdır.\n"
"\n"
"Şifreyi girdiyseniz, doğru olduğundan emin olun.\n"
"\n"
"Aksi takdirde, lütfen NVDA konfigürasyonlarına, TesseractOCR seçeneklerine "
"gidin ve 'Parola sor' onay kutusunu işaretleyin."

#. Translators: Message to be announced during Keyboard Help
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:321
msgid "Performs OCR to focused file in File Explorer"
msgstr "Dosya Gezgini'nde odaklanmış dosyaya OCR gerçekleştirir"

#. Translators: Announcing we are not in File Explorer and the key stroke will not do anything...
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:330
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:396
msgid "You are not in File Explorer to perform OCR on a image file..."
msgstr ""
"Bir görüntü dosyası üzerinde OCR gerçekleştirmek için Dosya Gezgini'nde "
"değilsiniz..."

#. Translators: Asking to wait untill the process is concluded
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:344
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:360
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:378
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:410
msgid "Processing... Please wait... This operation can takes some seconds..."
msgstr "İşleniyor... Lütfen bekleyin... Bu işlem birkaç saniye sürebilir..."

#. Translators: Informing that the file is not from supported types...
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:367
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:415
msgid "File not supported"
msgstr "Dosya desteklenmiyor"

#. For translators: Message to be announced during Keyboard Help
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:371
msgid "Performs OCR to a document on the scanner"
msgstr "Tarayıcı kullanarak taranan belgeye OCR işlemi uygulanır"

#. Translators: Message to be announced during Keyboard Help
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:388
msgid "Gets the text from focused accessible PDF file in File Explorer"
msgstr "Dosya Gezgini'nde odaklanmış erişilebilir PDF dosyasından metni alır"

#. Translators: Message to be announced during Keyboard Help
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:419
msgid "Cancel scanning"
msgstr "Taramayı iptal eder"

#. Translators: Informing user the process was terminated
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:441
msgid "Scanning process terminated!"
msgstr "Tarama işlemi sonlandırıldı!"

#. Translators: Asking user to enter the PDF password
#: addon\globalPlugins\tesseractOCR\__init__.py:453
msgid "Enter your password"
msgstr "Parolanızı girin"

#. Add-on summary/title, usually the user visible name of the add-on
#. Translators: Summary/title for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in add-on store
#: buildVars.py:21
msgid "TesseractOCR: An OCR add-on"
msgstr "TesseractOCR: Bir OCR eklentisi"

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-on store
#: buildVars.py:24
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Performs OCR on the selected image file, PDF, JPG, TIF, etc, or  a "
#| "document through a scanner and also can get the text from an accessible "
#| "PDF file.\n"
#| "The results are shown in a text file.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Windows+Control+r - Performs OCR to the selected image file\n"
#| "Windows+Control+w - Scans and recognize the document in the scanner\n"
#| "Windows+Control+t - To get the text from an accessible PDF\n"
msgid ""
"Performs OCR on the selected image file, PDF, JPG, TIF, etc, or  a document "
"through a scanner and also can get the text from an accessible PDF file.\n"
"The results are shown in a text file.\n"
"\n"
"Windows+Control+r - Performs OCR to the selected image file\n"
"Windows+Control+w - Scans and recognize the document in the scanner\n"
"Windows+Control+t - To get the text from an accessible PDF"
msgstr ""
"Seçilen görüntü dosyası, PDF, JPG, TIF, vb. veya bir tarayıcı aracılığıyla "
"bir belge üzerinde OCR gerçekleştirir ve ayrıca erişilebilir bir PDF "
"dosyasından metni alabilir.\n"
"Sonuçlar bir metin dosyasında gösterilir.\n"
"\n"
"Windows+Control+r - Seçilen görüntü dosyasına OCR gerçekleştirir\n"
"Windows+Control+w - Tarayıcıdaki belgeyi tarar ve tanır\n"
"Windows+Control+t - Erişilebilir bir PDF'den metin almak için\n"

#. Brief changelog for this version
#. Translators: what's new content for the add-on version to be shown in the add-on store
#: buildVars.py:34
msgid ""
"Set compatibility with NVDA 2026.1.\n"
"Updated TesseractOCR to 5.5.0.\n"
"Updated XPDF to 4.0.6.\n"
"It is again possible to choose the scanner to use.\n"
"With Tesseract 5.5 the image orientation is automatically made by "
"Tesseract.\n"
"So, the document type \"Only paper orientation\" only announce the "
"orientation of the image.\n"
" Now, it only runs on 64-bits machines.\n"
" Some bugs were corrected."
msgstr ""

